NEW AFFORDABLE HOMES IN TWICKENHAM
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    Twenty nine new shared ownership and sixteen affordable rented
    properties were officially opened yesterday in Twickenham
    town centre.

    The development is called Queens House, on Holly Road in
    Twickenham. Thanks to 550,000 pounds of additional support from the
    Council, the building was purchased by Thames Valley Housing
    Association (TVHA) and transformed into modern, high quality, low
    cost homes to buy targeted at local residents and workers on middle
    to low incomes.

